      "title": "Leader of \u2018Ape Jana Bala Pakshaya\u2019 arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Saman Perera, the leader of \u2018Ape Jana Bala Pakshaya\u2019 (Our Power of People Party or OPPP), has been arrested for harbouring a suspect allegedly involved in a murder.",
        "According to reports, the murder had taken place on the 5th of June in Kudawella."
